client_candidates.comment: budget reasons - we are going to handle the QA with our existing internal QA person. Responsibilities: QA engineer are focused on functional testing, mainly on QA regression testing to prevent defects in production and find the source of new bugs.

Worked on the PDP product page (detailed product page) for the Brass Monkey website. 
Redesigned the homepage for the Basic Pleasure Mode site, made a desktop and mobile version. 
Fixed some page edits. 
Further worked on Spell of Love jewelry site, made a popup for quick purchase of goods on the page for desktop and mobile version, made it in several versions, when the goods are in stock, not in stock and where there are many variants of colors/sizes, also worked on banners for the site. 
Finalized edits to the site.  
Then there was a task for the site Herbalgardens.co.uk, redesigned the block with the benefits of the product.  
Worked on the Farmiloe website, redesigned the “About Us” page with all the blocks and made a “About Brands” page with the 8 brands Farmiloe works with. 
Made several variants of blocks placement, made design for desktop and mobile version.
